OL,3,C'He stole his victim's childhoods':
OL,4,CPaedophile teacher jailed for sex
OL,5,Coffences
OL,7,FA former Trowbridge school teacher and
OL,8,Fchurch choirmaster has been convicted
OL,9,Fof 32 sexual offences against at least
OL,10,Fsix young boys.
OL,12,FRobert Kalton, 88 and of Ashby Road in
OL,13,FBurton upon Trent, worked at St
OL,14,FAugustine's Roman Catholic School.
OL,16,FHe was sentenced to four years in
OL,17,Fprison for the non-recent child sex
OL,18,Foffences at Salisbury Crown Court on
OL,19,F15 February.
