OL,3,C'He stole his victim's childhoods':
OL,4,CPaedophile teacher jailed for sex
OL,5,Coffences
OL,7,FKalton pleaded guilty to four counts
OL,8,Fof gross indecency with a boy under
OL,9,Fthe age of 14 and two counts of gross
OL,10,Findecency with a boy under the age of
OL,11,F16 at a previous hearing at Salisbury
OL,12,FCrown Court on 24 November.
OL,14,FThe court heard that at the time the
OL,15,Finvestigation commenced Kalton was
OL,16,Falready serving a four-year prison
OL,17,Fsentence for similar offending.
OL,19,FHis crimes span two decades and he
OL,20,Foperated in various locations across
OL,21,Fthe UK.
