OL,3,C'He stole his victim's childhoods':
OL,4,CPaedophile teacher jailed for sex
OL,5,Coffences
OL,7,FThe victim in this case came to police
OL,8,Fin December 2019 and reported that
OL,9,FKalton, who was a maths teacher at a
OL,10,FCatholic secondary school in
OL,11,FTrowbridge, had abused him multiple
OL,12,Ftimes over five years when he was aged
OL,13,Fbetween 11 and 16 years old, with
OL,14,Fthese offences dating back to the
OL,15,F1970s.
