OL,3,C'He stole his victim's childhoods':
OL,4,CPaedophile teacher jailed for sex
OL,5,Coffences
OL,7,FIn a statement released by his victim
OL,8,Fto the court, the former pupil said:
OL,9,F"Robert Kalton was a teacher. He was
OL,10,Falso a religious man. As such he had
OL,11,Fpower and respect. He occupied a
OL,12,Fposition of trust, and he abused that
OL,13,Ftrust in the worst way possible.
OL,15,F"School is a place where you spend a
OL,16,Flarge proportion of your childhood. It
OL,17,Fis a place where you should feel safe.
OL,18,FInstead, I was made to dread and fear
OL,19,Fgoing to school."
