OL,3,C'He stole his victim's childhoods':
OL,4,CPaedophile teacher jailed for sex
OL,5,Coffences
OL,7,FAt the hearing Kalton was sentenced to
OL,8,Ffour years for one count of indecent
OL,9,Fassault on a boy under 14. On three
OL,10,Ffurther counts of indecent assault on
OL,11,Fa boy under 14 he received sentences
OL,12,Fof 20 weeks, two years, and two years
OL,13,Frespectively.
OL,15,FOn two counts of indecent assault on a
OL,16,Fman aged 16 or over he received one
OL,17,Fyear and one year respectively. The
OL,18,Fsix sentences will run concurrently.
OL,20,FHe is also on the sex offenders
OL,21,Fregister for life.
