OL,3,C'He stole his victim's childhoods':
OL,4,CPaedophile teacher jailed for sex
OL,5,Coffences
OL,7,FDetective Sergeant Rachel Winter of
OL,8,FWiltshire Police said: "Robert Kalton
OL,9,Fis a sexual predator who used his
OL,10,Fposition of authority as a teacher and
OL,11,Fmember of the Catholic church to
OL,12,Fsystematically abuse young boys.
OL,14,F"He stole his victim's childhoods and
OL,15,Fchanged their lives forever. They have
OL,16,Flived with what happened to them for
OL,17,Fmany years, and undoubtedly the crimes
OL,18,Fcommitted have affected them ever
OL,19,Fsince.
