OL,7,F"The victim in this case has shown
OL,8,Fimmense courage throughout the
OL,9,Finvestigation and legal proceedings.
OL,10,FIt is their perseverance which has
OL,11,Fresulted in the conviction.
OL,13,F"This case also highlights that no
OL,14,Fmatter the length of time that has
OL,15,Fpassed, the public should feel
OL,16,Freassured that we will thoroughly
OL,17,Finvestigate non-recent offences and
OL,18,Fsupport and work with victims
OL,19,Fthroughout".
